snippet.title: It Lives - Super Mario Bros Dimensions 2 (Part 4)
snippet.description:
Download now at https://mfgg.net/index.php?act=resdb&param=02&c=2&id=36132

Super Mario Bros. Dimensions 2 is the upcoming sequel to Super Mario Bros. Dimensions. Taking place after the end of the first game, the Mushroom Kingdom is intruded upon by the dangerous EVL Army, who steal the powerful ring that Bowser had used in the last game. Mario, Luigi and Polter are joined by an ex-EVL soldier named Eden to take back Princess Peach and the ring!
